  "description": {
    "zh": "啊…经典老枪 —— AKM，一切的开始……\n\n但站在你枪口下的人可不会觉得怀旧，他们只会后悔来到了塔科夫。\n\n我给你安排好了地方，去 ULTRA 商场里做测试，那地方四通八达、近战频发，正合适。\n你在里面不会迷路吧？小心点，那里可是常年有伏击。\n\n别忘了把 Valday 光学瞄具装上，完成后回来找我领报酬。",
    "en": "A classic - the AKM, what it all started...\n\nThe people who are gonna stand at the receiving end of your barrel won't have such a good time, let me assure you that!\n\nI got the perfect place for you to test this machine, in the ULTRA shopping mall! You are able to navigate around inside there, right? Never let your guard down inside there, trust me.\n\nYour rifle needs to be equipped with a valday optic. Come back when you're done."
  },
